{"tid":1468403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場佔領行動方向討論","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:40.000Z","uid":65981,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"97ec4cfb14acfc3be666848c0e3e3a1d6a5f25bf","tid":1468403,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:19.000Z","msg":"依兩日癱瘓機場有好多突發嘢出來，而無統一共識之下開始有混亂情況。其中最大既問題係機場由「和理非」轉咗「停你飛」，有輿論話影響到依兩日要返屋企既外國旅客或者有急事去外地既人，有可能影響到民意。<br />\n<br />\n依嫁想做個投票，睇下大家認為有無必要將行動升級，用其他方式阻止離境，定維持本來佔領arrival hall，比來緊去機場既手足一個參考。<br />\n<br />\n正評比「和你飛」<br />\n負評比「停你飛」"},{"pid":"cafe20f78d1dd05b92cbd1186b25da931780e52c","tid":1468403,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">試下用 我不會放棄機場 回覆</span>"},{"pid":"e51280dc503039109b61b9aa5d12ea224029d87b","tid":1468403,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:51.000Z","msg":"負"},{"pid":"97c8e33eb4aa5e21ab6d479b6698a81eef414041","tid":1468403,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>唔割席</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民間記者會要AM開</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果大量的道歉，跟政府形成對比，可能仲有得救</span></span><br />\n3日不入機場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3022668%2Friot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=3c72e155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Court 出左injunction ，而家係FC唔到，聽日仲入去既，自己睇路，<br />\n林鄭就係想拎定&ldquo;法庭授權警察清機場&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算無injunction，入去輸多獲? 運動立即壽終正寢"},{"pid":"64b3f63e6bc0b0d519202870103e1f67e0d8dcc9","tid":1468403,"uid":180168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔夠人就接機<br />\n無謂隔硬黎<br />\n況且已經有新聞話出禁制令<br />\n應該想阻都阻唔到"},{"pid":"714faae3e21413d5fe7654873aab1edffe471496","tid":1468403,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即時停止停你飛，全人道歉，保持正常機場運作</span>"},{"pid":"43ce6704fa3cb1d1d5f29e86f996181309296630","tid":1468403,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:35:12.000Z","msg":"維持但唔應該「主動」阻<br />\n夠多人就自然「被動」阻<br />\n唔夠多人就對外宣傳"},{"pid":"c1cffaee6281ffd243f00ca0ea711c807b04f24a","tid":1468403,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:35:21.000Z","msg":"另外，依兩日林鄭既回應擺明佢對我地癱瘓機場既做法束手無策，唯有出經濟同感情牌，將矛頭帶返落示威者度，造成民眾對立，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我建議民宣／民間記者會可以再發起deadline，通知唔同國家既航空公司，喺九月一日前政府再無回應，將會無限期佔領機場，叫佢地慎重考慮取消九月之後既航班</span>，咁樣既可以避免有外國旅客滯留香港既情況，同時避免流失民意。<br />\n<br />\n為咗方便追post，如果有人對deadline有意見可以直接reply依度作討論"},{"pid":"81ef31b37caa872b5744309ac6a08315da617308","tid":1468403,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場三不<br />\n不衝突 不打人<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(打狗同還手唔計)</span> 不入禁區</span>"},{"pid":"22dd77f1d4cb38009ade7cd96b8ce7672da3ffc6","tid":1468403,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔夠人&gt;&gt;&gt;和你飛<br />\n多人&gt;&gt;&gt;停你飛"},{"pid":"616f4b6b913d21610fcd31d0177ff8ba914197e2","tid":1468403,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:40.000Z","msg":"我揀「停你飛」, 不過淨係停中国人飛, 唔停其他外國遊客"},{"pid":"be8f778f3f10a142eff227872dda7177c7a4dc5d","tid":1468403,"uid":24496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"今日我都有份謎謎糊糊咁停你飛<br />\n仲用係動畫學返嚟嘅日文同啲日本客解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗返起其實都幾on9<br />\n冇錯，停左你飛的確可以make noise, 啲旅客可以搵大使館求救etc<br />\n不過你估下人地國家會屌鳩港共定屌鳩你地阻人出人嘅人先？<br />\n老閪都想搞走你地班人去確保自己國民嘅安全先<br />\n咁停你飛法連本來嘅朋友都會變埋敵人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟愚見，聽日準備硊玻璃了"},{"pid":"8e037fcb163cd5354163a35df4c9d1c56b8d67d7","tid":1468403,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22dd77f1d4cb38009ade7cd96b8ce7672da3ffc6","tid":1468403,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔夠人&gt;&gt;&gt;和你飛<br />\n多人&gt;&gt;&gt;停你飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"其實理論上無得咁做<br />\n我地某程度上已經成為咗一大team<br />\n如果每次行動措施都唔一樣 好易有位比人入<br />\n同埋真係會搞到無辜既旅客"},{"pid":"68abe54850c08e80805b6a94b6332da005050244","tid":1468403,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6baf2603dddcc9b83ff0c5a849492134693634b9","tid":1468403,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}